lead_paragraph: Emese Hof scored six of her 15 points in overtime and No. 18 Miami closed the game with a 13-0 run to defeat Virginia Tech 67-56 on Sunday.

headline.print_headline: Hof Leads No. 18 Miami Women to 67-56 OT Win Over Va Tech
